{"tid":1189724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"他們有5艘航母...美推動取消中國「發展中國家」特權","createTime":"2019-06-07T02:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T03:14:05.000Z","uid":39464,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bffe8368c811b19bf6b0dc671a022506a771b6be","tid":1189724,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T02:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yc5fBgo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyc5fBgo.png&h=404ed2db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕在世界貿易組織（WTO）中，中國為「發展中國家」，享有種種優惠，美國對此感到不滿，有美國國會議員透露，美國政府正在推動取消中國發展中國家的地位。<br />\n<br />\n《美國之音》報導，美國眾議院外交委員會亞太小組委員會主席約霍（Ted Yoho）指出，美國國會與政府正在推動取消中國發展中國家的地位，他諷刺「這個國家是世界第二大經濟體，他們建造5艘航空母艦，他們透過一帶一路在全球投資，他們還發展太空項目，怎麼可能是發展中國家」。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，今年1月，美國就曾向世貿組織遞交文件，要求取消部分發展中國家的差別待遇，美國總統川普也持續對中國列為發展中國家一事發表批評。至於中方則堅稱，中國雖然是第二大經濟體，但從人均GDP、教育水準來看是發展中國家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2814946\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2814946&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=40b53c12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2814946&h=72441bcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2814946</a>"},{"pid":"8f4ffe62dd326c310e39282431469b5f25840790","tid":1189724,"uid":195944,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T02:37:21.000Z","msg":"公字我贏 字就你輸<br />\n<br />\n結論 狆蟈又燃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母啦死蝗蟲 咁撚有錢都話自己發展中<br />\n<br />\n你老母個閪啲閪毛就發展中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d19d667e4864111708fe45ecd156fe2ee8dfa9f","tid":1189724,"uid":41961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T02:38:34.000Z","msg":"中國永遠是發展中國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c029d153727bc44dd971d293c5074c07cf8c02","tid":1189724,"uid":5026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T02:38:36.000Z","msg":"習近平：無論將來中國怎麼發展，都永遠屬於發展中國家"},{"pid":"48b89b83b4b205ea807737713adce51164f83cdf","tid":1189724,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T02:38:41.000Z","msg":"堵塞漏洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100209657122a5f4ec0a6f06824b2e22cd60a57f","tid":1189724,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T02:39:27.000Z","msg":"平時要認叻認屁 而家全世界尊重你 應該開心至係"},{"pid":"2b4951f1b45dc13f2fc65e6679f60f39d1324a39","tid":1189724,"uid":51612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:13:54.000Z","msg":"正完大種乞衣"},{"pid":"c85c5ac98aa00873f93550d75f944f983663294f","tid":1189724,"uid":51612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b4951f1b45dc13f2fc65e6679f60f39d1324a39","tid":1189724,"uid":51612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:13:54.000Z","msg":"正完大種乞衣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:14:05.000Z","msg":"正宗"}]}